delete_inst_space_group(25.10)                  delete_inst_space_group(25.10)

Name
       delete_inst_space_group  -  Deletes  instance space group by a specific
       group name

Syntax
       delete_inst_space_group

       [-help]

       <groupName>

       Deletes instance space group by a specific group name.

Parameters
       <groupName>
              Specifies the name of the group.

       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes type and  default  in-
              formation for each delete_inst_space_group parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man delete_inst_space_group.

